Which means the person
is still reacting

00:28:07.680 --> 00:28:09.084 align:middle line:90%
to the same past event.

00:28:09.084 --> 00:28:11.500 align:middle line:84%
Now, if you keep that refractory
period going on for years

00:28:11.500 --> 00:28:14.210 align:middle line:84%
on end, that's called
a personality trait.

