00:33:39.380 --> 00:33:41.480 align:middle line:84%
to break that habit
of being yourself.

00:33:41.480 --> 00:33:42.375 align:middle line:90%
Take a look.

00:33:42.375 --> 00:33:43.000 align:middle line:90%
>>DISPENZA: Hi.

