was how do we do this.

00:36:28.790 --> 00:36:32.510 align:middle line:84%
So science is the contemporary
language of mysticism.

00:36:32.510 --> 00:36:36.470 align:middle line:84%
And because we can use science
to demystify the mystical,

00:36:36.470 --> 00:36:38.850 align:middle line:84%
it gives every person
the opportunity

00:36:38.850 --> 00:36:41.510 align:middle line:90%
to experiment in their life.

00:36:41.510 --> 00:36:43.650 align:middle line:84%
So can you believe
in a future that you

00:36:43.650 --> 00:36:47.860 align:middle line:84%
can't see or experience
with your senses yet,

