And to live by this law is to
live by the quantum law, which

00:37:31.720 --> 00:37:35.470 align:middle line:84%
says that the environment
is an extension of our mind.

00:37:35.470 --> 00:37:39.430 align:middle line:84%
And when we truly change
our mind, our life changes.

